1
00:00:19,690 --> 00:00:26,890
♪Lights of swords are like
a splash of rivers♪

2
00:00:27,280 --> 00:00:34,320
♪Shadows of swords cover the seasons♪

3
00:00:34,700 --> 00:00:38,090
♪The clear water cuts off the gorge♪

4
00:00:38,910 --> 00:00:42,190
♪Which is facing the armed army♪

5
00:00:42,410 --> 00:00:45,780
♪Missing a pot of cold wine♪

6
00:00:46,520 --> 00:00:49,590
♪Drunk in the middle of sand♪

7
00:00:49,670 --> 00:00:53,520
♪The place of peace of mind
is my hometown♪

8
00:00:54,280 --> 00:00:57,240
♪But my hometown is by your side♪

9
00:00:57,240 --> 00:01:01,520
♪Who forgets about the grudges
in the past♪

10
00:01:01,830 --> 00:01:04,920
♪Don’t blame the west wind
for your tears♪

11
00:01:04,920 --> 00:01:08,700
♪To meet and to part are like a dream♪

12
00:01:09,430 --> 00:01:12,610
♪Well-armed with armor and weapons♪

13
00:01:12,610 --> 00:01:16,960
♪Where the surging river is going♪

14
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:22,960
♪Together we go to the end of the world♪

15
00:01:24,380 --> 00:01:29,980
=Legend of Fei=

16
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:32,940
=Episode 18=

17
00:01:33,550 --> 00:01:35,040
Luckily,

18
00:01:35,360 --> 00:01:39,080
I ran into two people
and they led the way for me.

19
00:01:46,080 --> 00:01:47,760
How do you know

20
00:01:47,760 --> 00:01:49,230
they would come to me?

21
00:01:49,230 --> 00:01:51,640
We met by chance.

22
00:01:52,310 --> 00:01:53,550
Just by looking at her,

23
00:01:54,270 --> 00:01:57,060
I know she practiced her
internal strength in a wrong way.

24
00:01:59,310 --> 00:02:01,310
In Hengyang,

25
00:02:01,310 --> 00:02:04,910
only Madam Nichang’s

26
00:02:04,910 --> 00:02:07,300
Floating Palm can cure her.

27
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:09,750
In that case,

28
00:02:09,750 --> 00:02:12,090
you are just in time.

29
00:02:12,750 --> 00:02:14,320
You choose the perfect timing

30
00:02:14,320 --> 00:02:16,830
to take advantage of us.

31
00:02:16,830 --> 00:02:18,640
Madam, you are indeed smart.

32
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:21,450
This girl is badly hurt.

33
00:02:23,110 --> 00:02:25,620
Even for the sake of Li Zheng,

34
00:02:26,630 --> 00:02:28,760
you won’t just let her die.

35
00:02:30,910 --> 00:02:32,420
You are impressive.

36
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:34,880
You did nothing

37
00:02:34,880 --> 00:02:37,040
and cost me most of my power.

38
00:02:37,670 --> 00:02:40,110
You deserve the name of
the Head of Demons.

39
00:02:40,110 --> 00:02:41,630
You are sinister, treacherous,

40
00:02:41,630 --> 00:02:43,910
and extremely shameless.

41
00:02:44,720 --> 00:02:47,160
But there is one thing
I don’t understand.

42
00:02:47,160 --> 00:02:48,600
Why did you

43
00:02:48,600 --> 00:02:50,750
take all these efforts

44
00:02:50,750 --> 00:02:52,160
just to see me, a little singer?

45
00:02:53,550 --> 00:02:55,750
I’m here today

46
00:02:55,750 --> 00:02:58,720
because I have something to ask you.

47
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:02,670
Do you know

48
00:03:02,670 --> 00:03:04,440
the Color of Ocean and Heaven?

49
00:03:08,190 --> 00:03:09,580
I have never heard of it.

50
00:03:10,270 --> 00:03:12,170
What’s the Color of Ocean and Heaven?

51
00:03:15,470 --> 00:03:18,600
Madam, let’s not do this the hard way.

52
00:03:18,600 --> 00:03:19,600
Go.

53
00:03:41,670 --> 00:03:44,270
With your current power,

54
00:03:44,270 --> 00:03:46,520
I’m afraid you can’t protect everyone
in Qiaoyun House.

55
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:47,640
That’s enough!

56
00:03:50,880 --> 00:03:51,930
Shen Tianshu.

57
00:03:53,390 --> 00:03:55,340
Believe it or not,

58
00:03:56,320 --> 00:03:57,750
I only know
that the Color of Ocean and Heaven

59
00:03:57,750 --> 00:03:59,750
is a huge place of treasure.

60
00:03:59,750 --> 00:04:00,750
That’s only because

61
00:04:00,750 --> 00:04:02,520
I heard some elders talk about it.

62
00:04:03,550 --> 00:04:06,080
But the Color of Ocean and Heaven
concerns the world.

63
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:07,360
I really don’t know

64
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:08,520
where it is

65
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:09,710
and what’s inside.

66
00:04:11,440 --> 00:04:12,370
Is it?

67
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:15,870
Madam, you’d better tell me the truth.

68
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:19,270
I don’t want to be never able to see

69
00:04:19,270 --> 00:04:22,140
the performance of Yuyi Troupe again.

70
00:04:23,510 --> 00:04:26,670
No matter how you threaten me with them,

71
00:04:26,670 --> 00:04:28,760
I have nothing else to tell you.

72
00:04:29,320 --> 00:04:31,120
Shen Tianshu, I need to warn you.

73
00:04:31,920 --> 00:04:33,760
Don’t be too wild.

74
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:36,040
This is Hengyang,

75
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:38,110
not your Demons Manor.

76
00:04:38,110 --> 00:04:39,270
The garrison of Lord Gantang

77
00:04:39,270 --> 00:04:40,730
is not far from Hengyang.

78
00:04:41,790 --> 00:04:43,040
If you have to

79
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:45,570
make a scene today,

80
00:04:45,950 --> 00:04:48,990
my Yuyi Troupe will be there for you!

81
00:04:53,640 --> 00:04:54,400
Good.

82
00:04:55,510 --> 00:04:59,290
I will take your words this time.

83
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:19,860
Sorry for bothering you.

84
00:05:21,070 --> 00:05:25,010
I’ll come to enjoy the Yuyi Troupe’s
performance some other day.

85
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:28,480
Any time.

86
00:05:34,550 --> 00:05:36,610
Master, take the medicine.

87
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:54,440
Master, Mr. Qian Suiyou
wants to see you.

88
00:05:55,160 --> 00:05:56,230
You may leave.

89
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:04,000
What’s the matter?

90
00:06:05,270 --> 00:06:07,160
Thank you for saving Fei.

91
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:08,820
My appreciation is beyond words.

92
00:06:09,640 --> 00:06:11,340
I’ll be at your disposal

93
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:13,080
if the Yuyi Troupe needs me.

94
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:16,570
You don’t need to thank me.

95
00:06:17,200 --> 00:06:19,060
I didn’t do it for you.

96
00:06:22,200 --> 00:06:23,390
Back then,

97
00:06:24,070 --> 00:06:26,090
Zhou Fei’s grandfather
was my good friend.

98
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:29,020
My friend’s granddaughter was injured.

99
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:31,460
How could I stand by?

100
00:06:32,550 --> 00:06:34,040
No matter who you did it for,

101
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:35,120
you still did me a big favor.

102
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:41,780
You seem to have deep feelings
for Miss Zhou.

103
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:47,790
All right.

104
00:06:48,760 --> 00:06:50,620
Let’s drop the empty gesture.

105
00:06:53,350 --> 00:06:54,950
There is something

106
00:06:54,950 --> 00:06:56,800
that I want to know.

107
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:58,670
Madam, please go ahead.

108
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:05,550
Recently I heard

109
00:07:05,550 --> 00:07:07,570
there is some turbulence

110
00:07:08,270 --> 00:07:10,950
relevant to the descendants
of South Blade.

111
00:07:10,950 --> 00:07:12,230
I think you should have gone through

112
00:07:12,230 --> 00:07:13,720
those things.

113
00:07:14,670 --> 00:07:16,730
That’s what you are talking about.

114
00:07:18,200 --> 00:07:19,440
I would like to know

115
00:07:19,440 --> 00:07:21,070
the details of the whole story

116
00:07:21,070 --> 00:07:22,520
and the truth.

117
00:07:25,230 --> 00:07:26,180
Some time ago,

118
00:07:26,670 --> 00:07:29,330
Timber Wolf of Demons, Shen Tianshu
showed up in Four-guardian Mountain.

119
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:32,140
Then Huo’s Manor suffered an accident.

120
00:07:32,950 --> 00:07:34,720
Huo Liantao fled away.

121
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:36,030
And Old Master Huo passed away.

122
00:07:38,200 --> 00:07:39,920
Shen Tianshu?

123
00:07:41,550 --> 00:07:43,430
Why did he show up
in Four-guardian Mountain?

124
00:07:44,670 --> 00:07:45,790
I heard

125
00:07:45,790 --> 00:07:47,160
that he covets Huo’s kicking techniques,

126
00:07:47,160 --> 00:07:48,550
so he went to kill them.

127
00:07:48,550 --> 00:07:49,620
But I don’t think

128
00:07:50,270 --> 00:07:52,720
the rumors are true.

129
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:54,540
He is the Lord of Demons Manor.

130
00:07:55,070 --> 00:07:56,230
There is no way he would lay his eyes on

131
00:07:56,230 --> 00:07:58,300
Huo’s special kicking techniques.

132
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:02,380
By the way,

133
00:08:02,950 --> 00:08:04,390
there is another thing.

134
00:08:04,390 --> 00:08:05,920
After the death of General Wang Lin,

135
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:08,110
his family members
were robbed and killed.

136
00:08:08,640 --> 00:08:10,040
Who sent the killer?

137
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:11,040
The Blessed Dog,

138
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:12,390
Qiu Tianjin.

139
00:08:24,880 --> 00:08:26,940
This is confusing.

140
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:30,510
Yeah.

141
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:32,360
They are just orphans and widows.

142
00:08:33,150 --> 00:08:36,020
Why would he send a big falcon
to hunt them down?

143
00:08:38,150 --> 00:08:39,070
So?

144
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:41,390
The Color of Ocean and Heaven.

145
00:08:45,590 --> 00:08:46,790
I’m afraid the people of Demons Manor

146
00:08:46,790 --> 00:08:49,350
have been looking for it
for a long time.

147
00:08:49,670 --> 00:08:51,740
Shen Tianshu got nothing useful today.

148
00:08:52,590 --> 00:08:53,520
I’m afraid there will be

149
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:56,760
a bloody storm.

150
00:08:58,590 --> 00:08:59,750
That’s ridiculous.

151
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:04,030
It’s despicable to

152
00:09:04,030 --> 00:09:05,840
harm the innocent

153
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:06,930
just for the hearsay.

154
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:11,080
There are people killing to get it.

155
00:09:11,080 --> 00:09:12,350
But they don’t know

156
00:09:12,350 --> 00:09:15,130
the Color of Ocean and Heaven
is useless to them.

157
00:09:19,280 --> 00:09:21,350
If everyone thinks like you do,

158
00:09:22,230 --> 00:09:23,530
the world can be at peace.

159
00:09:29,520 --> 00:09:32,320
When Shen Tianshu mentioned
the Color of Ocean and Heaven,

160
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:34,590
you didn’t seem to be surprised.

161
00:09:36,230 --> 00:09:37,560
Who do you belong to?

162
00:09:41,880 --> 00:09:42,780
Wang Lin?

163
00:09:45,400 --> 00:09:46,010
No.

164
00:09:47,880 --> 00:09:49,480
You are Zhou Yitang’s person.

165
00:09:52,520 --> 00:09:53,760
My surname is Xie.

166
00:09:53,760 --> 00:09:54,970
My name is Yun.

167
00:09:55,520 --> 00:09:56,130
I’m Xie Yun.

168
00:09:59,230 --> 00:10:00,340
Xie Yun?

169
00:10:02,230 --> 00:10:03,320
It’s getting late.

170
00:10:03,320 --> 00:10:04,530
I’ll leave you to rest.

171
00:10:05,280 --> 00:10:06,070
Thanks again.

172
00:10:07,110 --> 00:10:07,820
I won’t see you out.

173
00:10:14,910 --> 00:10:16,270
Xie Yun.

174
00:10:20,540 --> 00:10:25,980
(Qiaoyun House)

175
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:49,880
Fei, you are awake!

176
00:10:56,350 --> 00:10:57,090
How are you feeling?

177
00:11:00,590 --> 00:11:02,200
How’s Madam Nichang doing?

178
00:11:03,470 --> 00:11:04,230
Madam Nichang

179
00:11:04,230 --> 00:11:06,000
took the secret pill
made by Yuyi Troupe.

180
00:11:06,000 --> 00:11:06,670
She is resting

181
00:11:06,670 --> 00:11:07,760
in seclusion these days.

182
00:11:07,760 --> 00:11:08,840
She should be fine.

183
00:11:09,550 --> 00:11:11,080
Rest assured.

184
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:12,110
Just get better,

185
00:11:12,110 --> 00:11:14,140
only in this way won’t you
waste Madam’s efforts.

186
00:11:21,490 --> 00:11:23,500
Did Shen Tianshu come?

187
00:11:25,440 --> 00:11:27,960
What Madam Nichang said is true.

188
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:29,790
Shen Tianshu has got
the information here,

189
00:11:29,790 --> 00:11:30,980
he probably won’t come again.

190
00:11:34,840 --> 00:11:35,820
Seriously, how are you feeling now?

191
00:11:36,590 --> 00:11:38,850
Are you sure you are okay?

192
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:42,760
Does it still hurt?

193
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:44,910
Are you all right?

194
00:11:47,960 --> 00:11:49,710
You are energetic now.

195
00:11:49,710 --> 00:11:50,800
You should be fine.

196
00:11:53,550 --> 00:11:54,420
I’m thirsty.

197
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:55,530
I’ll get some water for you.

198
00:12:31,470 --> 00:12:32,370
I’m hungry.

199
00:12:33,440 --> 00:12:35,440
Let’s go. I’ll take you to the tea house
to grab a bite.

200
00:12:36,080 --> 00:12:38,150
I’ll get your clothes for you.
Wait for me.

201
00:12:47,280 --> 00:12:50,030
How long did I sleep?

202
00:12:52,820 --> 00:12:58,540
(Fortress of the Forty-Eight)

203
00:13:14,550 --> 00:13:15,410
Madam.

204
00:13:22,860 --> 00:13:27,740
(The Secret Service defected)

205
00:13:38,790 --> 00:13:41,150
Sir, do you have rooms?

206
00:13:41,150 --> 00:13:42,470
Sirs.

207
00:13:42,470 --> 00:13:43,710
We are the only one inn

208
00:13:43,710 --> 00:13:45,110
within a radius of dozens of miles.

209
00:13:46,080 --> 00:13:46,900
Well...

210
00:13:53,030 --> 00:13:54,910
One good room!

211
00:13:54,910 --> 00:13:55,850
-Two rooms!
-Two rooms!

212
00:13:58,960 --> 00:13:59,880
Two rooms.

213
00:13:59,880 --> 00:14:03,470
That’s not enough for two rooms.

214
00:14:08,910 --> 00:14:09,640
Waiter!

215
00:14:10,350 --> 00:14:12,530
Two good rooms!

216
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:15,400
No problem. I’m coming!

217
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:17,410
Sirs, please go upstairs!

218
00:14:21,420 --> 00:14:25,060
(Hongfu Inn)

219
00:14:31,910 --> 00:14:33,400
I’m done. Come in.

220
00:14:53,470 --> 00:14:55,910
What a beauty.

221
00:14:55,910 --> 00:14:57,590
My heart aches

222
00:14:57,590 --> 00:14:59,420
at the sight of you.

223
00:15:10,030 --> 00:15:11,190
Where are my clothes?

224
00:15:13,760 --> 00:15:15,660
Why do you want me to dress like this?

225
00:15:16,840 --> 00:15:17,930
Where are my clothes?

226
00:15:20,590 --> 00:15:22,030
Your clothes are dirty.

227
00:15:22,030 --> 00:15:23,410
It’s inappropriate to wear them.

228
00:15:23,910 --> 00:15:25,350
You look good

229
00:15:25,350 --> 00:15:26,480
in this dress.

230
00:15:32,910 --> 00:15:34,350
Stop watching me, let’s go.

231
00:15:36,520 --> 00:15:38,520
Do you want to go out with this hair?

232
00:15:38,520 --> 00:15:39,440
Or what?

233
00:15:39,440 --> 00:15:41,230
Come on, let me comb your hair.

234
00:15:41,230 --> 00:15:42,230
Sit down.

235
00:15:42,230 --> 00:15:43,400
Let me comb your hair.

236
00:15:46,670 --> 00:15:47,440
Yun.

237
00:15:47,440 --> 00:15:48,590
You know,

238
00:15:48,590 --> 00:15:50,580
I hate to see a beauty being wasted.

239
00:15:52,550 --> 00:15:53,140
Tell me,

240
00:15:53,520 --> 00:15:54,660
what kind of hairstyle do you want?

241
00:15:56,230 --> 00:15:57,590
Cross Bun?

242
00:15:57,590 --> 00:15:58,760
Feitian Bun?

243
00:15:58,760 --> 00:15:59,440
Or

244
00:16:04,280 --> 00:16:05,020
Lingyun Bun?

245
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:10,110
How about this?

246
00:16:11,520 --> 00:16:13,020
The Falling Bun is also pretty.

247
00:16:15,080 --> 00:16:16,790
You need to move less
after I get you this hairstyle.

248
00:16:16,790 --> 00:16:18,760
Otherwise, it will get loose in a while.

249
00:16:39,350 --> 00:16:41,280
Mr. Xie.

250
00:16:41,280 --> 00:16:44,280
Even you know how to dress up a beauty,

251
00:16:44,280 --> 00:16:46,550
you don’t need to
practice your skill on me.

252
00:16:55,760 --> 00:16:57,400
I have no ambitions.

253
00:16:57,400 --> 00:16:58,640
I don’t want to be a scholar

254
00:16:58,640 --> 00:17:00,150
nor a general.

255
00:17:00,150 --> 00:17:01,790
I just want to be a maid

256
00:17:01,790 --> 00:17:03,620
to comb my future wife’s hair.

257
00:17:07,560 --> 00:17:08,280
How is it?

258
00:17:15,880 --> 00:17:16,830
It’s ugly.

259
00:17:18,310 --> 00:17:19,800
I think it’s pretty.

260
00:17:28,810 --> 00:17:29,710
I mean,

261
00:17:31,430 --> 00:17:32,640
why do you have to wear this?

262
00:17:33,230 --> 00:17:34,950
You finally dress up

263
00:17:34,950 --> 00:17:36,160
and you have to cover yourself?

264
00:17:37,950 --> 00:17:39,490
It’s like walking at night
in fancy clothes.

265
00:17:40,190 --> 00:17:41,290
It’s too ugly.

266
00:17:45,710 --> 00:17:46,370
Fine.

267
00:17:46,830 --> 00:17:47,970
Don’t just eat.

268
00:17:48,590 --> 00:17:49,400
The clothes I borrowed

269
00:17:49,400 --> 00:17:51,110
would break if you keep eating.

270
00:17:51,110 --> 00:17:52,280
That’s because

271
00:17:52,280 --> 00:17:53,710
you borrowed such a dress.

272
00:17:53,710 --> 00:17:54,940
I feel awkward.

273
00:17:56,110 --> 00:17:58,000
I think it’s pretty.

274
00:18:05,640 --> 00:18:06,880
I mean,

275
00:18:06,880 --> 00:18:08,680
don’t just eat.

276
00:18:08,680 --> 00:18:10,350
You escaped from death this time.

277
00:18:10,350 --> 00:18:11,640
Have you reflected about it?

278
00:18:11,640 --> 00:18:12,950
Will you still pretend
to be tough again?

279
00:18:17,230 --> 00:18:18,510
Do you hear me?

280
00:18:19,160 --> 00:18:20,310
Got it.

