00:45:08,840 --> 00:45:10,760
Because he is my grandfather.

838
00:45:10,760 --> 00:45:11,950
You call him your grandfather.

839
00:45:11,950 --> 00:45:13,840
And you said you are not
a descendant of South Blade.

840
00:45:13,840 --> 00:45:15,040
You want to fool me?

841
00:45:15,520 --> 00:45:17,600
He is my grandfather,
not your grandfather.

842
00:45:17,600 --> 00:45:19,840
I can say whatever I want.
It’s none of your business.

843
00:45:19,840 --> 00:45:21,390
Listen,

844
00:45:21,390 --> 00:45:23,320
if you dare to touch me,

845
00:45:23,320 --> 00:45:25,520
the entire Fortress of the Forty-Eight
will never let you go!

846
00:45:25,520 --> 00:45:26,360
I don’t care!

847
00:45:27,760 --> 00:45:29,280
Why do you pull your blade that rashly?

848
00:45:29,280 --> 00:45:30,800
How can you treat a girl like that?

849
00:45:39,010 --> 00:45:42,520
♪Stars flow like river♪

850
00:45:43,580 --> 00:45:47,180
♪My yearning falls into the river♪

851
00:45:47,750 --> 00:45:51,820
♪Now that you’re in my life♪

852
00:45:52,070 --> 00:45:55,710
♪I will never be alone♪

853
00:45:55,710 --> 00:45:59,830
♪I haven’t seen the mountains with you♪

854
00:46:00,250 --> 00:46:04,680
♪Nor have I tied up your hair♪

855
00:46:05,340 --> 00:46:09,900
♪We haven’t finished our story in chaos♪

856
00:46:10,130 --> 00:46:14,760
♪The blade hasn’t been returned♪

857
00:46:14,950 --> 00:46:18,780
♪I fear not to roam the world with you♪

858
00:46:19,000 --> 00:46:23,690
♪When I go across the world for you♪

859
00:46:23,950 --> 00:46:27,690
♪I’m willing to shed blood for you♪

860
00:46:28,020 --> 00:46:33,110
♪Don’t mind whose land it is♪

861
00:46:33,110 --> 00:46:37,050
♪Where is home to the snowflake♪

862
00:46:37,050 --> 00:46:41,580
♪Come and melt in my embrace♪

863
00:46:42,200 --> 00:46:49,300
♪The spring sun is an invisible armor
that’ll hold♪

864
00:46:50,040 --> 00:46:54,670
♪The purest love is unadorned♪
